  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "While EIP-1559 transactions don't have a `gasPrice` field, it was decided to keep it as part of the JSON-RPC interface when returning txs, because of backwards compatibility with the tooling ecosystem.\r\n\r\nWe should return the right value there, which is not too complex, but not as trivial as it used to be. An explanation can be found [here](https://twitter.com/TimBeiko/status/1413535578545479682).",
